foods.ingredients: CRUST: WATER, WHOLE WHEAT FLOUR, ENRICHED WHEAT FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, MALTED BARLEY FLOUR, NIACIN, IRON, THIAMINE MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), CAULIFLOWER FLOUR, PALM OIL, PARMESAN CHEESE (PART-SKIM MILK, CULTURES, SALT, ENZYMES), YEAST, SOYBEAN OIL, SUGAR, SALT, OAT FIBER, GARLIC, NONFAT MILK, SPICES. FILLING: VEGETABLE BLEND (GREEN AND RED BELL PEPPER, BROCCOLI, MUSHROOM, ONION), REDUCED FAT MOZZARELLA CHEESE (PART-SKIM MILK, NONFAT MILK, CULTURES, SALT, VITAMIN A PALMITATE, ENZYMES), PARMESAN CHEESE (PART-SKIM MILK, CULTURES, SALT, ENZYMES), NATURAL FLAVOR.
